reviewText:
This game was offered to me by paradox, it's a fun but quite complex strategy game, but quite enjoyable, while the game tries to be realistic it should have quite more options, i feel like there is a need for more creativity.

-Should have some new overhauled  mechanics for trade, yet it should be quite simple to understand, more competitive race to be a religious head (more options for this also), conclusion: Improve ways to get to the top without war and conquest;
-enhanced AI;
-more appealing expansions..;
-Should be beyond sandbox game;
-Innovative quests;

I give it a 8.2/10

ps: EU IV is quite better than EU III, but could have been quite better for my taste.
